# ─── DO NOT COMMIT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local-only narrative reference. Anonymized but never to be published — even
# anonymized exchanges could be reverse-correlated by people who were in the
# original group. Keep ignored. If you ever need to share this repo as a
# tarball / zip, make sure these files aren't in the bundle either.
data/chat_anonymized.txt
data/chat_raw.txt
data/themes.md
data/participants.json
data/keywords.json
data/topics.json
/tmp_chat/

# Anchor/annotation file — collegamenti tra scenari e fonti (chat + cronaca
# pubblica). Visibili in locale come popup ℹ accanto ai titoli, MAI online.
# Contengono frasi parafrasate della chat che, anche se anonimizzate,
# potrebbero essere riconoscibili da chi era nel gruppo originale.
data/annotations.json
